snippet.title: Gears 5 - Official Hivebusters Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the trailer for the upcoming Hivebusters expansion for Gears 5. 

Explore the tropical Galangi islands, battle enemies with the team's ultimate abilities, and confront a deadly new predator when the expansion launches on December 15, 2020.
